title: Spectacles Gate
story: fever-dream
description: Verify wearing spectacles opens the down exit

---

# Start in receiving room
> look
[OK: contains "Receiving Room"]

# Take and wear spectacles
> take spectacles
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> wear spectacles
[OK: contains_any "wear" "put on" "Worn" "spectacles"]

# Go to corridor
> east
[OK: contains "Corridor"]

# Now down should work
> down
[OK: contains "Stairwell"]
